fields.name: Hario Filter unbleached Paper for 02 Dripper x 100
fields.description: The key to brewing a perfect cup is to ensure that you rinse the 02 Hario filter papers with hot water prior to adding the grounds into the dripper. You should  pour the hot water carefully onto the grounds without touching the paper filter.
